cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with a distributed adaptive scheme for multi-agent systems, which involves control theory and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves the use of adaptive algorithms, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper proposes a novel distributed scheme, which could be considered as a contribution to the field of machine learning, and hence, cs.LG (Machine Learning) could also be a possible category.
